<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-1q8mTJOASx8j1Au+a5WDVnPi2lkFfwwEAa8hDDdjZlpLegxhjVME1fgjWPGmkzs7" crossorigin="anonymous">
      <!-- Optional theme -->
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css" integrity="sha384-fLW2N01lMqjakBkx3l/M9EahuwpSfeNvV63J5ezn3uZzapT0u7EYsXMjQV+0En5r" crossorigin="anonymous">

      
      <link href = "stylesheets/login.css">
      
</head>
<body style = "background-color: #f2f2f2;padding-top: 12px;">




<div class="container">
  <div class = "row">
  <div class = "col-md-3"></div>
  <div class = "col-md-6">  

  <h1 id = "title"> Exonian Encounters <img src="images/lenny.png" alt="Smiley face" height="42" align="top"></h1>

  <div  class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-body">
  
   
<h2 style = "margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px" class="form-signin-heading">Sign in</h2>
  <form class="form-signin" id="local-sign-in" action="/login" method="post">
        
        <label for="inputEmail" class="sr-only">Email address</label>
        <input name = "email" type="text" id="inputEmail" class="form-control" placeholder="email@exeter.edu" required autofocus>
        <label for="inputPassword" class="sr-only">Password</label>
        <input name = "password" type="password" id="inputPassword" class="form-control" placeholder="Exeter Password or password key" required>
        

        <button style = "margin-top: 15px;"class="btn btn-lg btn-primary btn-block" type="submit">Sign in</button>
    </form>

<hr style = "margin-bottom: 30px;">
    <h3 class="form-signin-heading">Get Password Key </h3>
    <p>So I know its super sketchy to ask for your exeter password, since I could be phishing you. However, all I'm doing is testing if you could log into Exeter Connect. However, if your nervous about it, <b>enter your email and you'll get sent a new password key</b> to log in. But trust me, I'm not trying to get kicked out.</p>
    
    
   <form  action="/emailpass" method="post" >
   <div class="input-group">
      <input type="text" class="form-control" name = "email" placeholder="<% if(emailstatus == "noexist"){ %>No Email Found<% }else{ %>email@exeter.edu<% } %>">
       <span class="input-group-btn">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success" type="button">

        <% if(emailstatus == "sent"){ %>
          Sent <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok" aria-hidden="true"></span> 
        <% }else{ %>
          Send Password
        <% } %>

        </button>
      </span>
    </div><!-- /input-group -->
    </form>



      </div>
  </div>
</div>
  <div class = "col-md-3"></div>
      
</div> <!-- /container -->



</body>
</html>

